00307 void FusionCHPLegacyData::CreateAdapter()
00308 {
00309         if (adapter)
00310                 return;
00311 
00312         // Create a Calvin adapter
00313         IFusionCHPDataAdapter* calvinAdapter = new CalvinCHPDataAdapter();
00314         if (calvinAdapter)
00315         {
00316                 calvinAdapter->SetFileName(filename);
00317                 if (calvinAdapter->CanReadFile())
00318                 {
00319                         adapter = calvinAdapter;
00320                         header.Clear();
00321                         header.adapter = calvinAdapter;
00322                 }
00323                 else
00324                 {
00325                         delete calvinAdapter;
00326                         IFusionCHPDataAdapter* gcosAdapter = new GCOSCHPDataAdapter();
00327                         if (gcosAdapter)
00328                         {
00329                                 gcosAdapter->SetFileName(filename);
00330                                 if (gcosAdapter->CanReadFile())
00331                                 {
00332                                         adapter = gcosAdapter;
00333                                         header.Clear();
00334                                         header.adapter = gcosAdapter;
00335                                 }
00336                                 else
00337                                 {
00338                     adapter = 0;
00339                                         UnableToOpenFileException e;
00340                     if(gcosAdapter!= NULL)
00341                         delete gcosAdapter;
00342                     gcosAdapter = 0;
00343                                         throw e;
00344                                 }
00345                         }
00346                         else
00347                         {
00348                 adapter = 0;
00349                                 UnableToOpenFileException e;
00350                 if(gcosAdapter!= NULL)
00351                     delete gcosAdapter;
00352                 gcosAdapter = 0;
00353                                 throw e;
00354                         }
00355                 }
00356         }
00357 }
